cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.AI 

This paper deals with a wireless caching network, which is a subfield of networked systems (cs.NI). The proposed solution involves deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The problem of cache update is modeled as a Markov decision process, which is a subfield of control systems (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.IT, and cs.AI.
